<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>438</hymn_number>
<title>NI BANG A CEUMI KHUA CH438</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ni bang a ceumi khua a si, Vancung khuatha chung khi, Nitlak lonak ram
 ceunak cu, Khamhtu Jesuh a si.

[C1]
   A vailam kan put ahcun, (A vailam kan put ahcun), Sui luchin kan
   hmuh lai, (Sui luchin kha kan hmuh lai), Vancung khua kan phak tikah,
   (Vancung khua kan, phak tikah), A zungzal in kan ceu lai.

[V2]
 Vancung khua ah hnangam a um, Thihnak tiva ral ah, Tihnung vialte a
 lohnak ah, Khi khin kan ro a um.

[C2]
   A vailam kan put ahcun, (A vailam kan put ahcun), Sui luchin kan
   hmuh lai, (Sui luchin kha kan hmuh lai), Vancung khua kan phak tikah,
   (Vancung khua kan, phak tikah), A zungzal in kan ceu lai.

[V3]
 Pathian remhmi inn dawh bik cu, Mithiang umnak a si, Kan dawt ngaingai
 mi hna nih khan, Khikhin an kan don lai.

[C3]
   A vailam kan put ahcun, (A vailam kan put ahcun), Sui luchin kan
   hmuh lai, (Sui luchin kha kan hmuh lai), Vancung khua kan phak tikah,
   (Vancung khua kan, phak tikah), A zungzal in kan ceu lai.

[V4]
 Vawlei cung tih-phannak vialte, Zokzok in lonh ka duh, Vancung
 mithiang mi sinah khin, Thihnak a um lai lo.

[C4]
   A vailam kan put ahcun, (A vailam kan put ahcun), Sui luchin kan
   hmuh lai, (Sui luchin kha kan hmuh lai), Vancung khua kan phak tikah,
   (Vancung khua kan, phak tikah), A zungzal in kan ceu lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>